name: Bad Monkey
overview: A detective turned restaurant inspector in Southern Florida is pulled into a world of greed and corruption after a tourist finds a severed arm while fishing. And yes, there's a monkey.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Andrew Yancy has been bounced from the Miami Police Department and is now a health inspector in the Keys. After stumbling upon a case that begins with a human arm fished up by tourists, he realizes that if he can prove murder, he'll be back in. He just needs to get past a trove of Floridian oddballs and one bad monkey.

episodes.name: The Floating-Human-Body-Parts Capital of America
episodes.overview: When tourists on a fishing charter in Key West, Florida, discover a human arm, suspended detective Andrew Yancy takes the case.

episodes.name: A Hundred Bucks Says You Won't
episodes.overview: Caitlin meets with Yancy to discuss her suspicions about her stepmother Eve. Yancy learns of Eve's secret boyfriend.

episodes.name: Nobody Said He Was Alvin Einstein
episodes.overview: Yancy and Rosa continue their search for more information about Nick. Caitlin confronts Eve, leading to a shocking revelation.

episodes.name: Nothing's Wrong with It, I Just Don't Need It Anymore
episodes.overview: A flashback reveals Eve and Nick's origins, how Yancy got suspended, and Nick and Izzy's nefarious business dealings.

episodes.name: That Damn Arm Is Back
episodes.overview: Yancy makes a crucial realization as he goes into hiding. The Dragon Queen asks Egg about Neville.

episodes.name: Yo, Would You Tell Ms. Chase I Still Love Her Like Crazy
episodes.overview: In need of help, Yancy turns to Rogelio. Bonnie goes on the run. The Dragon Queen confronts Nick and Eve.

episodes.name: A Total Cat Person
episodes.overview: Rogelio and Yancy find themselves in an explosive situation. Eve negotiates with the Dragon Queen.

episodes.name: The Russian Mob Is Very Active in Key West
episodes.overview: With Caitlin and Rosa's help, Yancy cooks up a new plan to get Nick and Eve back to Miami.

episodes.name: You Really Don't Want to Kill This Scrumptious Little Puppy
episodes.overview: Yancy learns that his plan has gone awry, leaving Rosa in danger. Eve and the Dragon Queen have a reckoning.

episodes.name: We're in the Memory-Making Business
episodes.overview: The aftermath of the reckoning has shocking repercussions.
